{"data":[{"name":"84:1","price":"जब आकाश फट जाएगा।","arabic":"إِذَا ٱلسَّمَآءُ ٱنشَقَّتۡ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5885,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"idhā al-samāu inshaqqat ","translations":["When","the sky","is split asunder","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["idhā","al-samāu","inshaqqat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,400],[2,400,3560],[3,3560,5515]]}},{"name":"84:2","price":"और अपने पालनहार के आदेश पर कान लगाएगा और यही उसके योग्य है।","arabic":"وَأَذِنَتۡ لِرَبِّهَا وَحُقَّتۡ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5886,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-adhinat lirabbihā waḥuqqat ","translations":["And has listened","to its Lord","and was obligated","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-adhinat","lirabbihā","waḥuqqat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1060],[2,1060,2210],[3,2210,3655]]}},{"name":"84:3","price":"तथा जब धरती फैला दी जाएगी।","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡأَرۡضُ مُدَّتۡ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5887,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-idhā al-arḍu muddat ","translations":["And when","the earth","is spread","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-idhā","al-arḍu","muddat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,610],[2,610,1510],[3,1510,2715]]}},{"name":"84:4","price":"और जो कुछ उसके भीतर है, उसे निकाल बाहर फेंक देगी और खाली हो जाएगी।","arabic":"وَأَلۡقَتۡ مَا فِيهَا وَتَخَلَّتۡ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5888,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-alqat mā fīhā watakhallat ","translations":["And has cast out","what","(is) in it","and becomes empty","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-alqat","mā","fīhā","watakhallat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1070],[2,1070,1430],[3,1430,2260],[4,2260,3965]]}},{"name":"84:5","price":"और अपने पालनहार के आदेश पर कान लगाएगी और यही उसके योग्य है।[1]","arabic":"وَأَذِنَتۡ لِرَبِّهَا وَحُقَّتۡ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5889,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"1. (1-5) इन आयतों में प्रलय के समय आकाश एवं धरती में जो हलचल होगी उसका चित्रण करते हुए यह बताया गया है कि इस ब्रह्मांड के विधाता के आज्ञानुसार ये आकाश और धरती कार्यरत हैं और प्रलय के समय भी उसी की आज्ञा का पालन करेंगे। धरती को फैलाने का अर्थ यह है कि पर्वत आदि खंड-खंड होकर समस्त भूमि चौरस कर दी जाएगी।","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-adhinat lirabbihā waḥuqqat ","translations":["And has listened","to its Lord","and was obligated","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-adhinat","lirabbihā","waḥuqqat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1040],[2,1040,2220],[3,2220,3805]]}},{"name":"84:6","price":"ऐ इनसान! निःसंदेह तू कठिन परिश्रम करते-करते अपने पालनहार की ओर जाने वाला है, फिर तू उससे मिलने वाला है।","arabic":"يَٰٓأَيُّهَا ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ إِنَّكَ كَادِحٌ إِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ كَدۡحٗا فَمُلَٰقِيهِ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5890,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"yāayyuhā al-insānu innaka kādiḥun ilā rabbika kadḥan famulāqīhi ","translations":["O","mankind","Indeed, you","(are) laboring","to","your Lord","(with) exertion","and you (will) meet Him","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["yāayyuhā","al-insānu","innaka","kādiḥun","ilā","rabbika","kadḥan","famulāqīhi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2600],[2,2600,4850],[3,4850,6230],[4,6230,7350],[5,7350,7890],[6,7890,8750],[7,8750,10220],[8,10220,13585]]}},{"name":"84:7","price":"फिर जिस व्यक्ति को उसका कर्मपत्र उसके दाहिने हाथ में दिया गया।","arabic":"فَأَمَّا مَنۡ أُوتِيَ كِتَٰبَهُۥ بِيَمِينِهِۦ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5891,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"fa-ammā man ūtiya kitābahu biyamīnihi ","translations":["Then as for","(him) who","is given","his record","in his right (hand)","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["fa-ammā","man","ūtiya","kitābahu","biyamīnihi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1840],[2,1840,2210],[3,2210,2990],[4,2990,4260],[5,4260,6055]]}},{"name":"84:8","price":"तो उसका आसान हिसाब लिया जाएगा।","arabic":"فَسَوۡفَ يُحَاسَبُ حِسَابٗا يَسِيرٗا","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5892,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"fasawfa yuḥāsabu ḥisāban yasīran ","translations":["Then soon","his account will be taken","an account","easy","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["fasawfa","yuḥāsabu","ḥisāban","yasīran",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,820],[2,820,1890],[3,1890,3080],[4,3080,5275]]}},{"name":"84:9","price":"तथा वह अपने लोगों की ओर ख़ुश-ख़ुश लौटेगा।","arabic":"وَيَنقَلِبُ إِلَىٰٓ أَهۡلِهِۦ مَسۡرُورٗا","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5893,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wayanqalibu ilā ahlihi masrūran ","translations":["And he will return","to","his people","happily","(9)"],"transliterationArr":["wayanqalibu","ilā","ahlihi","masrūran",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1990],[2,1990,3820],[3,3820,4880],[4,4880,6845]]}},{"name":"84:10","price":"और लेकिन जिसे उसका कर्मपत्र उसकी पीठ के पीछे दिया गया।","arabic":"وَأَمَّا مَنۡ أُوتِيَ كِتَٰبَهُۥ وَرَآءَ ظَهۡرِهِۦ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5894,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-ammā man ūtiya kitābahu warāa ẓahrihi ","translations":["But as for","(him) who","is given","his record","behind","his back","(10)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-ammā","man","ūtiya","kitābahu","warāa","ẓahrihi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1910],[2,1910,2300],[3,2300,3090],[4,3090,4450],[5,4450,6780],[6,6780,8105]]}},{"name":"84:11","price":"तो वह विनाश को पुकारेगा।","arabic":"فَسَوۡفَ يَدۡعُواْ ثُبُورٗا","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5895,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"fasawfa yadʿū thubūran ","translations":["Then soon","he will call","(for) destruction","(11)"],"transliterationArr":["fasawfa","yadʿū","thubūran",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,800],[2,800,1550],[3,1550,3215]]}},{"name":"84:12","price":"तथा जहन्नम में प्रवेश करेगा।","arabic":"وَيَصۡلَىٰ سَعِيرًا","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5896,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wayaṣlā saʿīran ","translations":["And he will burn","(in) a Blaze","(12)"],"transliterationArr":["wayaṣlā","saʿīran",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,970],[2,970,2695]]}},{"name":"84:13","price":"निःसंदेह वह अपने घर वालों में बड़ा प्रसन्न था।","arabic":"إِنَّهُۥ كَانَ فِيٓ أَهۡلِهِۦ مَسۡرُورًا","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5897,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"innahu kāna fī ahlihi masrūran ","translations":["Indeed, he","had been","among","his people","happy","(13)"],"transliterationArr":["innahu","kāna","fī","ahlihi","masrūran",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1690],[2,1690,2400],[3,2400,3990],[4,3990,5020],[5,5020,6925]]}},{"name":"84:14","price":"निश्चय उसने समझा था कि वह कभी (अल्लाह की ओर) वापस नहीं लौटेगा।","arabic":"إِنَّهُۥ ظَنَّ أَن لَّن يَحُورَ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5898,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"innahu ẓanna an lan yaḥūra ","translations":["Indeed, he","(had) thought","that","never","he would return","(14)"],"transliterationArr":["innahu","ẓanna","an","lan","yaḥūra",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1540],[2,1540,3130],[3,3130,3460],[4,3460,3900],[5,3900,7915]]}},{"name":"84:15","price":"क्यों नहीं, निश्चय उसका पालनहार उसे देख रहा था।[2]","arabic":"بَلَىٰٓۚ إِنَّ رَبَّهُۥ كَانَ بِهِۦ بَصِيرٗا","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5899,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"2. (6-15) इन आयतों में इनसान को सावधान किया गया है कि तुझे भी अपने पालनहार से मिलना है। और धीरे-धीरे उसी की ओर जा रहा है। वहाँ अपने कर्मानुसार जिसे दाएँ हाथ में कर्म-पत्र मिलेगा, वह अपनों से प्रसन्न होकर मिलेगा। और जिसको बाएँ हाथ में कर्म-पत्र दिया जाएगा, तो वह विनाश को पुकारेगा। यह वही होगा जिसने माया मोह में क़ुरआन को नकार दिया था। और सोचा कि इस सांसारिक जीवन के पश्चात कोई जीवन नहीं आएगा।","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"balā inna rabbahu kāna bihi baṣīran ","translations":["Yes","Indeed","his Lord","was","of him","All-Seer","(15)"],"transliterationArr":["balā","inna","rabbahu","kāna","bihi","baṣīran",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,730],[2,730,2480],[3,2480,3470],[4,3470,4130],[5,4130,4780],[6,4780,6485]]}},{"name":"84:16","price":"मैं क़सम खाता हूँ शफ़क़ (सूर्यास्त के बाद की लाली) की।","arabic":"فَلَآ أُقۡسِمُ بِٱلشَّفَقِ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5900,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"falā uq'simu bil-shafaqi ","translations":["But nay","I swear","by the twilight glow","(16)"],"transliterationArr":["falā","uq'simu","bil-shafaqi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2070],[2,2070,2890],[3,2890,4295]]}},{"name":"84:17","price":"तथा रात की और उसकी जो कुछ वह एकत्रित करती है!","arabic":"وَٱلَّيۡلِ وَمَا وَسَقَ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5901,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-al-layli wamā wasaqa ","translations":["And the night","and what","it envelops","(17)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-al-layli","wamā","wasaqa",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1050],[2,1050,1660],[3,1660,2695]]}},{"name":"84:18","price":"तथा चाँद की, जब वह पूरा हो जाता है।","arabic":"وَٱلۡقَمَرِ إِذَا ٱتَّسَقَ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5902,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-qamari idhā ittasaqa ","translations":["And the moon","when","it becomes full","(18)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-qamari","idhā","ittasaqa",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1130],[2,1130,1450],[3,1450,2585]]}},{"name":"84:19","price":"तुम अवश्य एक अवस्था से दूसरी अवस्था में स्थानांतरित होते रहोगे।","arabic":"لَتَرۡكَبُنَّ طَبَقًا عَن طَبَقٖ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5903,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"latarkabunna ṭabaqan ʿan ṭabaqin ","translations":["You will surely embark","(to) stage","from","stage","(19)"],"transliterationArr":["latarkabunna","ṭabaqan","ʿan","ṭabaqin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2340],[2,2340,3120],[3,3120,4410],[4,4410,5395]]}},{"name":"84:20","price":"फिर उन्हें क्या हो गया है कि वे ईमान नहीं लाते?","arabic":"فَمَا لَهُمۡ لَا يُؤۡمِنُونَ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5904,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"famā lahum lā yu'minūna ","translations":["So what","(is) for them","not","they believe","(20)"],"transliterationArr":["famā","lahum","lā","yu'minūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,630],[2,630,1160],[3,1160,1680],[4,1680,5015]]}},{"name":"84:21","price":"और जब उनके सामने क़ुरआन पढ़ा जाता है, तो सजदा नहीं करते।[3]","arabic":"وَإِذَا قُرِئَ عَلَيۡهِمُ ٱلۡقُرۡءَانُ لَا يَسۡجُدُونَۤ۩","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5905,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"3. (16-21) इन आयतों में ब्रह्मांड के कुछ लक्षणों को साक्ष्य स्वरूप प्रस्तुत करके सावधान किया गया है कि जिस प्रकार यह ब्रह्मांड तीन स्थितियों से गुज़रता है, उसी प्रकार तुम्हें भी तीन स्थितियों से गुज़रना है : सांसारिक जीवन, फिर मरण, फिर परलोक का स्थायी जीवन जिसका सुख-दुख सांसारिक कर्मों के आधार पर होगा।","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-idhā quri-a ʿalayhimu al-qur'ānu lā yasjudūna ","translations":["And when","is recited","to them","the Quran","not","they prostrate","(21)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-idhā","quri-a","ʿalayhimu","al-qur'ānu","lā","yasjudūna",""],"verseTiming":[[1,0,840],[2,840,1540],[3,1540,2580],[4,2580,4050],[5,4050,4530],[6,4530,8025]]}},{"name":"84:22","price":"बल्कि जिन्होंने कुफ़्र किया, वे (उसे) झुठलाते हैं।","arabic":"بَلِ ٱلَّذِينَ كَفَرُواْ يُكَذِّبُونَ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5906,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"bali alladhīna kafarū yukadhibūna ","translations":["Nay","Those who","disbelieved","deny","(22)"],"transliterationArr":["bali","alladhīna","kafarū","yukadhibūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,450],[2,450,1420],[3,1420,2250],[4,2250,6025]]}},{"name":"84:23","price":"और अल्लाह सबसे अधिक जानने वाला है जो कुछ वे अपने भीतर रखते हैं।","arabic":"وَٱللَّهُ أَعۡلَمُ بِمَا يُوعُونَ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5907,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-lahu aʿlamu bimā yūʿūna ","translations":["And Allah","(is) most knowing","of what","they keep within themselves","(23)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-lahu","aʿlamu","bimā","yūʿūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,950],[2,950,1750],[3,1750,2340],[4,2340,5065]]}},{"name":"84:24","price":"अतः उन्हें एक दर्दनाक यातना की शुभ सूचना दे दो।","arabic":"فَبَشِّرۡهُم بِعَذَابٍ أَلِيمٍ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5908,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"fabashir'hum biʿadhābin alīmin ","translations":["so give them tidings","of a punishment","painful","(24)"],"transliterationArr":["fabashir'hum","biʿadhābin","alīmin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2090],[2,2090,3240],[3,3240,6065]]}},{"name":"84:25","price":"परंतु जो लोग ईमान लाए तथा उन्होंने सत्कर्म किए, उनके लिए कभी न समाप्त होने वाला बदला है।[4]","arabic":"إِلَّا ٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُواْ وَعَمِلُواْ ٱلصَّٰلِحَٰتِ لَهُمۡ أَجۡرٌ غَيۡرُ مَمۡنُونِۭ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5909,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"4. (22-25) इन आयतों में उनके लिए चे